## Why add example files

The generator already supports override profiles and override templates. Example files make that feature easier to use.

Users should be able to look at `content/examples/overrides/`, copy it to their bundle or site-specific override directory, and make small edits.

Recommended runtime override location:

```text
/overrides/profiles/
/overrides/templates/
```

Recommended source example location in this repo:

```text
content/examples/overrides/
```

The examples should not be active by default. They are reference material only.

