## Optional example: testing the examples

After adding or changing examples, rebuild the test image and run:

```bash
podman run --rm \
  --entrypoint /usr/local/bin/pxe-content-test \
  registry.gitlab.us.lmco.com/lit/containers/pxe-content:test \
  all
```

Passing tests prove the image can generate, validate, preserve, overwrite, and serve PXE content without real PXE hardware.

They do not replace a real PXE boot test when boot behavior or install behavior changes.

