## Cleanup guidance

Before merging the final Phase 8 docs, check for these common cleanup items:

- Remove old generated sample files that are no longer used.
- Do not keep a static generated `index.html` if the Python generator creates it at runtime.
- Keep examples under `content/examples/` so they do not become active runtime profiles by accident.
- Keep active built-in profiles under `content/profiles/`.
- Keep active built-in templates under `templates/`.
- Keep test scripts under `tests/` and copy them into the image through the Dockerfile.
- Make sure test scripts have Unix line endings and executable permissions.
- Make sure the Dockerfile installs or includes any shell used by the scripts.